        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Cassata is a two-day cake. Bake the sponge and make the ricotta filling on day one, then assemble and refrigerate overnight. Decorate on day two. The "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termSlug": "pan-di-spagna",
                  "term": "Pan di spagna"
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "pan di spagna sponge"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " must be cold before assembly. Chill the filled cake before the marzipan and icing go on."
          }
        ]
      },
